## RAG Feature Analysis & Improvement Recommendations

### Current Architecture (End-to-End)

```
┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐
│ Two independent RAG paths:                                   │
│                                                              │
│ PATH A: Admin Chat (ai-chat.js → Groq LLM)                 │
│   User message → LLM decides to call search_knowledge_base  │
│   → getEmbedding (OpenAI text-embedding-3-small, 1536d)     │
│   → match_documents RPC (pgvector cosine, Supabase)         │
│   → Post-filter by threshold → Top 5 chunks (600 chars ea)  │
│   → LLM synthesizes answer                                  │
│                                                              │
│ PATH B: Bid Assistant Chat (sales.jsx → external backend)   │
│   User message → POST /api/bidding/.../chat {top_k: 6}     │
│   → Proxied to sw-bidding-api.vercel.app                    │
│   → Returns {answer, citations[]}                           │
│   → Displayed as chat bubbles with citation footnotes        │
└──────────────────────────
